<item>
	<title>Metrix Create:Space: Above are just a few examples of the beautiful jewelry that...</title>
	<guid>http://metrixcreatespace.com/post/1226008633</guid>
	<link>http://metrixcreatespace.com/post/1226008633</link>
	<description>&lt;img src=&quot;http://29.media.tumblr.com/tumblr_l9nb7ehJzl1qa5a6qo1_500.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://27.media.tumblr.com/tumblr_l9nb7ehJzl1qa5a6qo2_500.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://25.media.tumblr.com/tumblr_l9nb7ehJzl1qa5a6qo3_500.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://26.media.tumblr.com/tumblr_l9nb7ehJzl1qa5a6qo4_500.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;p&gt;Above are just a few examples of the beautiful jewelry that local crafter &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.audrawint.com/&quot;&gt;Audra Wint&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;has cut here at Metrix. Besides the fact we love that she’s a faithful regular, we really appreciate her design philosophy: make stuff that looks cool.&lt;/p&gt;
